title: Grateful Dead Live at Henry J. Kaiser Convention Center on 1986-12-31
description:
Set 1

Jack Straw
Sugaree
Me & My Uncle
Mexicali Blues
Candyman
Desolation Row
U.S. Blues

Set 2

Let It Grow

Gimme Some Lovin'
When Push Comes To Shove

In The Midnight Hour

David Crosby Opened
The Neville Brothers opened

Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Brent Mydland - Keyboards
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums
